Summary
The Job Vacancies module provides a complete system for managing job recruitment convocatorias with:

✅ Full CRUD operations for vacancies
✅ Complex state management with business rules
✅ File attachment and management
✅ Multi-profile support per vacancy
✅ Automatic audit logging
✅ Public and admin access levels
✅ Comprehensive validation and authorization
